::Striker::

Striker smiles as he feels Spears hand move over his body, leaning slightly 
back to look into her eyes. They were both covered with soot, and the Ark 
itself wasn't too clean either. An idea occurs to him, Striker looking into 
Spears' eyes.

"Hey, how about we go on a walk? I think it would be more sanitary than 
laying here..."
